1
00:00:05,240 --> 00:00:08,380
[Oh Min Seong: What is this?]

2
00:00:08,380 --> 00:00:11,210
[Taichi: Thank you.]

3
00:00:14,050 --> 00:00:16,210
[Oh Min Seong: Did they tell us
to write our name on this?]

4
00:00:16,210 --> 00:00:18,850
[Taichi: We just put it in, right?]

5
00:00:18,850 --> 00:00:20,380
[Oh Min Seong: We don't have to
write our names.]

6
00:00:20,380 --> 00:00:22,100
[Taichi: Yes, put it into the mailbox.]

7
00:00:22,100 --> 00:00:23,450
[Oh Min Seong: Ah.]

8
00:00:24,610 --> 00:00:25,900
[Lee Hyun Jun: Here.]

9
00:00:25,900 --> 00:00:27,210
[Cho Yun Jae: What is this?]

10
00:00:27,210 --> 00:00:28,220
[Lee Hyun Jun: What they talked about.]

11
00:00:28,220 --> 00:00:31,290
[Cho Yun Jae: Ah, that...]

12
00:00:35,570 --> 00:00:39,450
[Kim Han Gyeol: No matter who is eliminated,
I'm starting to get concerned.]

13
00:00:39,450 --> 00:00:42,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: I just can't choose at all.]

14
00:00:42,940 --> 00:00:46,450
[Cho Yun Jae: It's unreasonable to ask us to choose.]

15
00:00:46,450 --> 00:00:48,450
[Cho Yun Jae: How could they be so cruel?]

16
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:51,650
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm about to cry.]

17
00:00:51,650 --> 00:00:54,370
[Kim Han Gyeol: You're so F.]

18
00:00:54,370 --> 00:00:57,010
[Cho Yun Jae: I want to cry
because I'm afraid I'll be eliminated.]

19
00:00:57,010 --> 00:00:58,580
[Kim Han Gyeol: Tsk.]

20
00:00:58,580 --> 00:01:01,810
[Cho Yun Jae: Everything is possible.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

21
00:01:01,810 --> 00:01:03,860
[Kim Han Gyeol: If I'm eliminated, I'll pack]

22
00:01:03,860 --> 00:01:06,610
[Kim Han Gyeol: and take a taxi home immediately.]

23
00:01:06,610 --> 00:01:08,930
[Lee Hyun Jun: I would do the same.]

24
00:01:08,930 --> 00:01:12,740
[Cho Yun Jae: To be honest, I want to be eliminated.]

25
00:01:11,020 --> 00:01:12,740
Wh-What are you talking about?

26
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:14,210
[Cho Yun Jae: I should have this attitude.]

27
00:01:14,210 --> 00:01:16,370
[Kim Han Gyeol: No, Hyung, we are better than those that came before.]

28
00:01:16,370 --> 00:01:17,539
[Kim Han Gyeol: We have to stay here till the end.]

29
00:01:17,539 --> 00:01:20,930
[Cho Yun Jae: But I haven't stood firm yet.]

30
00:01:21,830 --> 00:01:25,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I really can't guess.] Who is the last?

31
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:28,920
[Lee Hyeong Jun: They have different opinions from me.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Same.]

32
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:32,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Everyone's opinion is different from mine.]

33
00:01:32,180 --> 00:01:35,770
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Who?]
[Kim Sun Wook: I don't know who'll be last.]

34
00:01:35,770 --> 00:01:40,289
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Right. Even someone I know]

35
00:01:40,289 --> 00:01:41,970
[Eum Hyeok Jin: can be the last place.]

36
00:01:41,970 --> 00:01:47,340
[Kim Sun Wook: That aside, everyone thinks differently now.]

37
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:50,009
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What? Who they think is 1st place?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yes.]

38
00:01:50,009 --> 00:01:52,330
[Lee Hyeong Jun: The last place is different too.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's right.]

39
00:01:52,330 --> 00:01:56,910
[Kim Sun Wook: So it's possible there will be many changes in the middle.]

40
00:01:57,380 --> 00:01:59,220
[Lee Hyeong Jun: That's possible.]

41
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:02,380
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It's unpredictable.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: For real.]

42
00:02:03,370 --> 00:02:06,010
[Park Jae Ha: How was your walk?]

43
00:02:06,010 --> 00:02:07,730
[Kim Su Min: The walk?]
[Park Jae Ha: Yes.]

44
00:02:07,730 --> 00:02:11,250
[Kim Su Min: It was good. Got some fresh air.]

45
00:02:11,250 --> 00:02:18,700
[Park Jae Ha: Why are you like a deflated balloon now?]
[Kim Su Min: Look at this envelope.]

46
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,780
[Park Jae Ha: Ah...]

47
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:24,620
[Kim Su Min: Hmm...]

48
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:31,260
[Park Jae Ha: So cruel.]

49
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:34,540
[Park Jae Ha: The one with the most votes gets eliminated, right?]

50
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:45,380
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Why are you looking so down?]

51
00:02:46,050 --> 00:02:49,060
[Park Jae Ha: Did you see this?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Ah...]

52
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:50,740
[Park Jae Ha: Take one each.]

53
00:02:50,740 --> 00:02:53,820
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Is this yours? Then this is mine.]
[Park Jae Ha: This is mine.]

54
00:02:55,579 --> 00:02:56,980
[Kim Su Min: It's too hard.]

55
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:58,250
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I don't want to do this.]

56
00:02:58,250 --> 00:03:02,080
[Park Jae Ha: Right. I really don't want to do it.]

57
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:08,780
[Kim Su Min, please go to the mailbox
to vote for who you like
the most to least
ranked from first to tenth.]

58
00:03:09,580 --> 00:03:11,220
[Kim Su Min: I'll get going.]

59
00:03:11,220 --> 00:03:13,100
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Go ahead.]

60
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:19,740
[Voting for who they like the most]

61
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:35,660
[Facing the inevitable reality,
their steps are heavy.]

62
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:53,140
[The difficult choice begins]

63
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,700
[Kim Su Min: This is really the hardest.]

64
00:03:59,700 --> 00:04:03,420
[Kim Su Min: To be honest, it's easy to rank the first few.]

65
00:04:03,420 --> 00:04:08,060
[Kim Su Min: But ranking those at the back is too difficult.]

66
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:10,940
[Kim Su Min: So I thought about it for a long time.]

67
00:04:10,940 --> 00:04:15,740
[Kim Su Min: What standards should I be ranking by?]

68
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:28,860
[Kim Sun Wook: Because we need to rank from 1st to 10th,]

69
00:04:28,860 --> 00:04:30,220
[Kim Sun Wook: something might happen to the 10th place]

70
00:04:30,220 --> 00:04:31,980
[Kim Sun Wook: if I were to rank someone 10th.]

71
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:36,940
[Kim Sun Wook: But I think there might still be a chance.]

72
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:48,220
[Lee Hyun Jun: I wanted to spoil my vote.]

73
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:51,500
[Lee Hyun Jun: Because the ranking means nothing to me.]

74
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,260
[Park Jae Ha: My standards are simple.]

75
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:03,440
[Park Jae Ha: First of all, Hyeong Jun ranks first as always.]

76
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:05,940
[Park Jae Ha: The rest are ranked based on how familiar I am with them—]

77
00:05:05,940 --> 00:05:08,760
[Park Jae Ha: people I am comfortable with.]

78
00:05:19,380 --> 00:05:24,220
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Just based on my preference,
someone might be eliminated.]

79
00:05:24,220 --> 00:05:27,440
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So I came up with a different standard.]

80
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:29,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I ranked people who don't seem]

81
00:05:29,340 --> 00:05:31,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: interested in me for the lower rankings.]

82
00:05:31,820 --> 00:05:35,880
[Lee Hyeong Jun: That's how I ranked the people.]

83
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:39,520
[Taichi: Oh what?]

84
00:05:44,300 --> 00:05:45,600
[Taichi: I did it as who I liked the most]

85
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,800
[Taichi: if it were our first meeting.]

86
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,100
[Taichi: The person I like the most.]

87
00:05:49,100 --> 00:05:51,659
[Taichi: The person I want to know more.]

88
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:08,260
[The men's votes stacking up
inside the mailboxes]

89
00:06:12,660 --> 00:06:15,530
[This is not a simple choice
as elimination is impending]

90
00:06:22,820 --> 00:06:26,180
[What kind of outcomes
will the men's choices bring?]

91
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:30,220
[The voting is over]

92
00:06:31,180 --> 00:06:35,580
[Kim Su Min: Because there will be people eliminated,]

93
00:06:35,580 --> 00:06:42,500
[Kim Su Min: I felt guilty when voting.]
[Park Jae Ha: There's no way you don't feel guilty...]

94
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,659
[Lee Hyeok Jin: My self-esteem has been low.]

95
00:06:47,659 --> 00:06:51,500
[Lee Hyeok Jin: As I'm feeling negative about everything,]

96
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:56,140
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I kept pushing myself
into the candidates to be eliminated.]

97
00:06:56,659 --> 00:06:59,220
[Kim Han Gyeol: I chose quickly.]

98
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:03,580
[Cho Yun Jae: Really?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: There are a few people who just don't exist to me.]

99
00:07:03,580 --> 00:07:07,340
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's a personal preference.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yes.]

100
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:11,140
[Cho Yun Jae: But I'm starting to get attached.]

101
00:07:12,300 --> 00:07:16,920
[Cho Yun Jae: I also ranked by how attached I am to the person.]

102
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:20,680
[Kim Han Gyeol: You're so emotional.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yes. I have feelings for everyone.]

103
00:07:23,260 --> 00:07:27,420
[Cho Yun Jae: From the beginning, I am only interested in Hyun Jun.]

104
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:29,420
[Cho Yun Jae: I know many people can see it.]

105
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:32,000
[Cho Yun Jae: People might think]

106
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,820
[Cho Yun Jae: cause I only think of Hyun Jun,]

107
00:07:34,820 --> 00:07:36,260
[Cho Yun Jae: I won't choose anyone else—]

108
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:39,840
[Cho Yun Jae: that's what I was most worried about.]

109
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:44,800
[Eum Hyeok Jin: They'll announce the candidates
to be eliminated later, right?]

110
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:47,500
[Kim Sun Wook: No idea. They might just announce who's eliminated.]

111
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:50,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Or would they just eliminate them without saying anything?]

112
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:52,440
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Would they just disappear like bubbles?]

113
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:56,340
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Whoever gets eliminated, it'd be a pity if they just disappear.]

114
00:07:56,340 --> 00:07:59,820
[Kim Sun Wook: The person who will be eliminated has been decided.]

115
00:07:59,820 --> 00:08:01,800
[Kim Sun Wook: The person eliminated is OOO.]

116
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:04,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's so scary.]

117
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:07,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I kept worrying if it would be me.]

118
00:08:07,140 --> 00:08:09,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: 'Cause I don't know how]

119
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:11,780
[Eum Hyeok Jin: people I already know would rank me,]

120
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:14,820
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and I am very well aware]

121
00:08:14,820 --> 00:08:16,380
[Eum Hyeok Jin: that I am not Han Gyeol's 1st place.]

122
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:18,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I'm really anxious.]

123
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:31,460
[Oh Min Seong: But how much you like someone is so subjective.]

124
00:08:31,460 --> 00:08:33,539
[Oh Min Seong: It's only my second day here.]

125
00:08:33,539 --> 00:08:35,340
[Oh Min Seong: And I'm the only one who came on the second day.]

126
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:38,220
[Oh Min Seong: They were familiar with each other.]

127
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:41,580
[Oh Min Seong: So the probability of me being eliminated might be higher.]

128
00:08:42,620 --> 00:08:45,300
[Park Jae Ha: Gosh.]

129
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:48,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun: How tiring.]

130
00:08:49,140 --> 00:08:52,260
[The sighs mix in with the silence]

131
00:08:56,420 --> 00:09:01,090
[A silent night for the men]

132
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:04,430
[The text the men are receiving
make them anxious again]

133
00:09:02,860 --> 00:09:03,620
Well...

134
00:09:04,450 --> 00:09:08,610
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So scary. So, so scary.]

135
00:09:12,530 --> 00:09:15,730
[The voting
for the eliminated person is over]

136
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:20,610
[Lee Hyun Jun: There are two eliminated?]

137
00:09:22,450 --> 00:09:26,930
[Interest ranking: 1st place (10 points)-10th place (1 point)
The scores are summed up to determine who is eliminated.
Two people will be eliminated through this vote.]

138
00:09:26,930 --> 00:09:29,810
[Lee Hyeok Jin: There will be people eliminated?]

139
00:09:31,610 --> 00:09:34,570
[Kim Su Min: Rather than just a candidate.]

140
00:09:34,690 --> 00:09:40,010
[Park Jae Ha: No wonder there are so many people this time.]

141
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:44,330
[Lee Hyeok Jin: How much are they going to torture us?]

142
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:46,180
This is crazy.

143
00:09:46,290 --> 00:09:48,570
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why are there two?]

144
00:09:48,570 --> 00:09:52,170
[Lee Hyeong Jun: They didn't say they'd only eliminate one.]

145
00:09:53,330 --> 00:09:56,100
[Kim Sun Wook: In a way,]

146
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,770
[Kim Sun Wook: I've only focused on one person]

147
00:09:57,770 --> 00:10:00,490
[Kim Sun Wook: and haven't really spoken to the others,]

148
00:10:00,490 --> 00:10:03,250
[Kim Sun Wook: so I might be eliminated too.]

149
00:10:08,090 --> 00:10:12,410
[Taichi: After learning that it's not just one but two made my stomach hurt.]

150
00:10:15,350 --> 00:10:19,410
[A result that no one could predict]

151
00:10:22,210 --> 00:10:27,290
[The male guests finally received the voting result]

152
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What is this?]

153
00:10:33,660 --> 00:10:36,840
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Gosh.]

154
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:45,140
[Kim Sun Wook: Does it... just end... like this?]

155
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:50,780
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Just pack and leave?]

156
00:10:57,480 --> 00:11:01,220
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I didn't expect it to be either of them.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Me too.]

157
00:11:01,220 --> 00:11:05,060
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I thought neither of them would be eliminated.]

158
00:11:21,460 --> 00:11:24,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: Oh?]

159
00:11:37,740 --> 00:11:43,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: These are people I didn't expect at all.
[Cho Yun Jae: Same.]

160
00:11:44,620 --> 00:11:47,400
[Cho Yun Jae: What to do?]

161
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:52,540
[Oh Min Seong: So scary. What's this even?]

162
00:11:52,540 --> 00:11:58,620
[Men's House]

163
00:12:03,140 --> 00:12:05,380
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Wow.]

164
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:10,140
[Park Jae Ha and Lee Hyeok Jin,
your journey at Men's House has come to an end.
Please leave Men's House immediately.]

165
00:12:20,660 --> 00:12:23,350
[Park Jae Ha: Ha...]

166
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:38,820
[Interest ranking: 11th place]

167
00:12:38,880 --> 00:12:42,900
[Park Jae Ha: I guess.]

168
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:45,420
[Park Jae Ha: But that's such a pity.]

169
00:12:45,420 --> 00:12:50,820
[Interest ranking: 10th place]

170
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:48,700
What a pity.

171
00:13:00,020 --> 00:13:06,360
[Park Jae Ha: I can't even cry. I've already used up my emotions.]

172
00:13:08,740 --> 00:13:11,280
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I was just about to start.]

173
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:37,280
[Park Jae Ha: Let's pack our bags.]

174
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:41,600
[Lee Hyeok Jin: We're moving out today, right?]

175
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:44,420
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Going home]

176
00:13:44,420 --> 00:13:47,460
[Lee Hyeok Jin: right now.]

177
00:13:50,660 --> 00:13:53,150
[Lee Hyeok Jin: This dating show is way too cruel.]

178
00:13:53,150 --> 00:13:57,360
[Park Jae Ha: It can't be helped. That's the rule.]

179
00:13:55,180 --> 00:13:56,100
Right.

180
00:13:57,360 --> 00:14:02,300
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I think I've tried my best.]

181
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:06,180
[Park Jae Ha: I'm worried about Hyeong Jun.]

182
00:14:06,180 --> 00:14:08,700
[Park Jae Ha: I hope he doesn't find it tiring.]

183
00:14:10,660 --> 00:14:15,180
[Kim Su Min: I can't say anything.]

184
00:14:15,180 --> 00:14:18,180
[Kim Su Min: I dare not comfort them.]

185
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:23,080
[Kim Su Min: I couldn't say anything at all.]

186
00:14:23,900 --> 00:14:26,320
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I still have a lot of things I want to do. Quite a pity.]

187
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:30,460
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I still have a lot to do. How am I already...]

188
00:14:30,460 --> 00:14:33,760
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Feels like I'm leaving too early.]

189
00:14:34,660 --> 00:14:36,910
[Park Jae Ha: Actually, I feel quite relieved.]

190
00:14:36,910 --> 00:14:39,700
[Park Jae Ha: Though it's a pity that I'm eliminated,]

191
00:14:39,700 --> 00:14:42,620
[Park Jae Ha: and that I don't have a happy ending]

192
00:14:42,620 --> 00:14:45,220
[Park Jae Ha: with Hyeong Jun through this program.]

193
00:14:45,220 --> 00:14:47,460
[Park Jae Ha: But that's just my personal regret.]

194
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:50,580
[Park Jae Ha: I'm more worried about Hyeong Jun.]

195
00:14:52,820 --> 00:14:54,780
[Please check your ranking in the mailbox.]

196
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:55,780
What is it?

197
00:14:55,580 --> 00:14:57,700
[Kim Sun Wook: It says we can check the mailbox.]

198
00:15:02,220 --> 00:15:03,900
[Kim Sun Wook: What is it?]

199
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:13,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You can see your total scores.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Are they asking us to take it away?]

200
00:15:13,140 --> 00:15:18,350
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's for us to see. I'm in 10th place. I'm doomed.]

201
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:21,350
[Kim Sun Wook: First of all, seeing I don't have any "10th"...]

202
00:15:21,350 --> 00:15:24,420
[Kim Sun Wook: I thought it seems like]

203
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:26,660
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm doing well.]

204
00:15:26,660 --> 00:15:30,320
[Kim Sun Wook: There are three "1st"s,]

205
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:32,660
[Kim Sun Wook: so I'm quite surprised.]

206
00:15:33,300 --> 00:15:37,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I didn't get 1st place.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Wait. I can't laugh at that.]

207
00:15:37,580 --> 00:15:39,220
[Kim Sun Wook: No. You said that so casually.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm so sad.]

208
00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:44,140
[Kim Sun Wook: Hide these quickly, Hyung.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why?]

209
00:15:44,820 --> 00:15:46,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I had only one thought.]

210
00:15:46,740 --> 00:15:52,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why didn't anyone pick me as 1st place?]

211
00:15:52,860 --> 00:15:55,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin] It's good to be someone's number one.

212
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:59,980
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I didn't get that, so I'm quite upset.]

213
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:03,880
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Take it out. Look inside.]

214
00:16:06,060 --> 00:16:10,140
[Kim Su Min: There were "8th," "9th," and also "2nd."]

215
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:13,260
[Kim Su Min: There were also a few mid-rankings.]

216
00:16:13,260 --> 00:16:19,200
[Kim Su Min: I was quite upset that I didn't get "1st."]

217
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:24,080
[Kim Su Min: But I was quite relieved I didn't get any "10th."]

218
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:27,280
[Kim Han Gyeol: Three people gave me "1st,"
and the rest were 9, 9, 9, 10, 10.]

219
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:30,800
[Kim Han Gyeol: That's when I knew people had]

220
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:34,280
[Kim Han Gyeol: very differing opinions about me.]

221
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:38,300
[Cho Yun Jae: I got "2nd" and "3rd."]

222
00:16:38,300 --> 00:16:44,300
[Cho Yun Jae: Why am I always 2nd?]

223
00:16:44,300 --> 00:16:46,180
[Cho Yun Jae: I kept thinking about that.]

224
00:16:46,180 --> 00:16:51,460
[Cho Yun Jae: Maybe I should take the initiative]

225
00:16:51,460 --> 00:16:53,980
[Cho Yun Jae: to get friendly with other people.]

226
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:57,980
[Taichi: I was quite happy.]

227
00:16:57,980 --> 00:17:01,220
[Taichi: I thought my result would be bad.]

228
00:17:01,220 --> 00:17:02,580
[Taichi: Even without "1st" and "2nd"s,]

229
00:17:02,580 --> 00:17:05,540
[Taichi: I'm happy with anything above "5th."]

230
00:17:05,540 --> 00:17:08,380
[Taichi: So I'm quite happy with the result, and I felt more confident.]

231
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:13,819
[Oh Min Seong: Why didn't I get any "1st"s? I didn't get any.]

232
00:17:13,819 --> 00:17:16,060
[Oh Min Seong: I thought someone would give me a "1st."]

233
00:17:16,060 --> 00:17:18,460
[Oh Min Seong: I was a little disappointed.]

234
00:17:18,460 --> 00:17:23,260
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I feel so stifled.]

235
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:30,140
[Men's House]

236
00:17:30,460 --> 00:17:32,780
[Park Jae Ha: What to do?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Gosh.]

237
00:17:32,780 --> 00:17:36,100
[Park Jae Ha: Hmm?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I just find it regretful.]

238
00:17:36,100 --> 00:17:40,460
[Park Jae Ha: What do you regret?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Everything from the start.]

239
00:17:40,940 --> 00:17:44,380
[Park Jae Ha: Everything right from the start?
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

240
00:17:44,610 --> 00:17:47,660
[Park Jae Ha: I don't have any regrets.]

241
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:52,780
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I put too much of my true feelings into this.]

242
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:57,860
[Park Jae Ha: I'm just worried.]

243
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:02,100
[Park Jae Ha: I'm just very worried.]

244
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:08,500
[Lee Hyeok Jin: They don't even give a chance. How merciless.]

245
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:13,060
[Park Jae Ha: What can we do?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: We can't even make one final struggle.]

246
00:18:13,060 --> 00:18:19,300
[Park Jae Ha: I find it a pity that I'm leaving without even a date with Hyeong Jun.]

247
00:18:25,010 --> 00:18:27,820
[Park Jae Ha: Where's Hyeong Jun?]

248
00:18:27,820 --> 00:18:31,380
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hyeong Jun is upstairs.]
[Park Jae Ha: Upstairs? Mm.]

249
00:18:36,260 --> 00:18:40,530
[Lee Hyeok Jin: At least give me a chance.]

250
00:18:44,340 --> 00:18:46,860
[Lee Hyeok Jin: What a pity.]

251
00:18:49,540 --> 00:18:50,580
[Kim Su Min: You just have to close it up, right?]

252
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:54,660
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yes, thank you.]

253
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:57,920
[Can't say anything to offer comfort]

254
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:16,220
[A difficult time for both those leaving
and those staying]

255
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:21,980
[The atmosphere in the room
is getting heavy]

256
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:53,160
[Lee Hyeok Jin: What did I do wrong?]

257
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:56,280
[Lee Hyeok Jin: What was my biggest problem?]

258
00:19:56,820 --> 00:19:59,450
[Lee Hyeok Jin: My self-esteem]

259
00:19:59,450 --> 00:20:01,240
[Lee Hyeok Jin: is at rock bottom right now.]

260
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:06,200
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I am completely helpless now.]

261
00:20:08,600 --> 00:20:10,360
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I'm frustrated.]

262
00:20:10,360 --> 00:20:13,700
[Lee Hyeok Jin: My pride is completely destroyed.]

263
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:23,120
["I feel so upset..."]

264
00:20:25,700 --> 00:20:26,620
Wait.

265
00:20:46,340 --> 00:20:51,090
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It's because of the show's rules.]

266
00:20:51,090 --> 00:20:53,200
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It's not their fault.]

267
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:56,380
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I hope they don't feel too guilty.]

268
00:20:56,380 --> 00:20:59,960
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I tried my best to act strong.]

269
00:21:01,020 --> 00:21:07,060
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I really look so pitiful.]
[Kim Sun Wook: No, no.]

270
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:22,100
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Even without me around, you have to do well.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yes.]

271
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:32,220
[Cho Yun Jae: Are you really leaving?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Leaving right now.]

272
00:21:32,820 --> 00:21:35,420
[Taichi: What is this?]

273
00:21:35,420 --> 00:21:37,020
[Cho Yun Jae: Oh gosh.]

274
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:41,420
[Taichi: Are you really leaving? I'll go outside with you.]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Yes.]

275
00:21:43,080 --> 00:21:45,260
[Cho Yun Jae: Bye.]

276
00:21:45,260 --> 00:21:48,020
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Meet you outside.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yes.]

277
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:51,460
[Kim Han Gyeol: Why?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I'm leaving right now.]

278
00:21:51,460 --> 00:21:55,100
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Be careful. Don't get hurt.]

279
00:21:55,100 --> 00:21:57,940
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Have a good time here.]

280
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:02,460
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Good luck, and let's meet again outside.]

281
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:05,140
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I'm leaving.]
[Taichi: I'll go with you.]

282
00:22:05,140 --> 00:22:06,580
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Good luck!]

283
00:22:08,300 --> 00:22:14,610
[Lee Hyeok Jin: All the best.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So annoying. Don't act like it's fine. It's so annoying.]

284
00:22:20,060 --> 00:22:25,070
[Oh Min Seong: It might be me next.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm really scared.]

285
00:22:25,070 --> 00:22:27,860
[Oh Min Seong: Really.]

286
00:22:29,100 --> 00:22:33,980
[Another man came to say goodbye]

287
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:46,330
[Park Jae Ha: Let's talk.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Okay.]

288
00:22:51,540 --> 00:22:54,380
[Park Jae Ha: Can I sit next to you?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hmm?]

289
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:56,060
[Park Jae Ha: Can I sit next to you?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yes.]

290
00:23:01,780 --> 00:23:06,380
[Park Jae Ha: I was just crying this morning saying I want to go home,
and here I am going home.]

291
00:23:13,940 --> 00:23:17,340
[Park Jae Ha: I'm sorry.]

292
00:23:19,860 --> 00:23:26,460
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Gosh, seriously.]

293
00:23:26,460 --> 00:23:28,720
[Park Jae Ha: Why?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Well...]

294
00:23:28,740 --> 00:23:31,710
[Lee Hyeong Jun: They did say there would be people eliminated.]

295
00:23:31,710 --> 00:23:35,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I knew someone would be eliminated.]

296
00:23:35,780 --> 00:23:38,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But I didn't expect Jae Ha to be eliminated.]

297
00:23:43,340 --> 00:23:47,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun: At that time, I wanted to talk to Jae Ha.]

298
00:23:47,780 --> 00:23:52,140
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Because I didn't know the ending.]

299
00:23:53,560 --> 00:23:59,140
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So I felt really sad.]

300
00:24:01,260 --> 00:24:05,860
[Park Jae Ha: Leaving Hyeong Jun alone,]

301
00:24:05,860 --> 00:24:08,820
[Park Jae Ha: I was worried. Very much so.]

302
00:24:08,820 --> 00:24:11,420
[Park Jae Ha: That he'd have a hard time.]

303
00:24:12,740 --> 00:24:17,770
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Ha...]
[Park Jae Ha: Why?]

304
00:24:17,770 --> 00:24:20,370
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Well...]

305
00:24:21,740 --> 00:24:26,850
[Feelings that he finds difficult
to put into words]

306
00:24:27,860 --> 00:24:35,700
[Lee Hyeong Jun: For three days,
I didn't say a word to him nor looked at him.]

307
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:39,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: That's why I felt so sorry towards him at that moment.]

308
00:24:42,340 --> 00:24:46,470
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Was it just because he was eliminated?]

309
00:24:48,970 --> 00:24:57,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Because he's suddenly leaving that I felt sorry?]

310
00:24:57,420 --> 00:25:00,700
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I keep thinking of what he said.]

311
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:11,420
["Can you give me another chance..."]

312
00:25:11,420 --> 00:25:19,660
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He's leaving when I haven't given him a chance yet.]

313
00:25:19,660 --> 00:25:25,740
[Lee Hyeong Jun: That made me very concerned.]

314
00:25:26,780 --> 00:25:31,220
[Taichi: Wah...]

315
00:25:29,780 --> 00:25:31,110
Everyone cried, right?

316
00:25:46,420 --> 00:25:50,740
[Taichi: Actually, when Jae Ha was filming before, they were a final couple.]

317
00:25:51,300 --> 00:25:54,260
[Oh Min Seong: During the previous shoot? Jae Ha?]

318
00:25:53,420 --> 00:25:53,860
Yes.

319
00:25:55,140 --> 00:25:59,580
[Oh Min Seong: Ichi said they were a final couple and had dated before.]

320
00:25:59,580 --> 00:26:02,020
[Oh Min Seong: I completely lost my mind.]

321
00:26:02,020 --> 00:26:08,500
[Oh Min Seong: It's fine they dated since that's a long time ago.]

322
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:16,100
[Oh Min Seong: Anyway, I can't help thinking more.]

323
00:26:18,860 --> 00:26:23,700
[Min Seong came to see Hyeong Jun]

324
00:26:38,310 --> 00:26:43,480
[Min Seong's eyes met with Jae Ha
who's with Hyeong Jun]

325
00:26:43,500 --> 00:26:47,980
[Park Jae Ha: Was that Min Seong just now?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yes.]

326
00:26:48,620 --> 00:26:52,300
[Min Seong turned around to leave
without saying anything]

327
00:26:52,340 --> 00:26:53,820
[Oh Min Seong: Both of them met my gaze.]

328
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:56,020
[Oh Min Seong: We looked at each other for a few seconds,]

329
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:59,380
[Oh Min Seong: and I closed the door and left.]

330
00:26:59,380 --> 00:27:02,280
[Oh Min Seong: I was angry looking at that scene.
Their fingers were interlocked—so angering.]

331
00:27:02,280 --> 00:27:04,100
[Oh Min Seong: How can I not be angry when I see that?]

332
00:27:04,100 --> 00:27:08,400
[Oh Min Seong: So is he serious about me?]

333
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:12,800
[Oh Min Seong: What is real? What is true?]

334
00:27:13,980 --> 00:27:16,850
[Oh Min Seong: What's going on between them?]

335
00:27:16,980 --> 00:27:17,910
What's going on?

336
00:27:18,500 --> 00:27:24,720
[Oh Min Seong: There's no one I can trust.]
[Cho Yun Jae: There's no one I can trust indeed.]

337
00:27:28,100 --> 00:27:32,470
[Min Seong's heart is stirring up]

338
00:27:32,470 --> 00:27:36,770
[Will Min Seong's love for Hyeong Jun
continue?]

339
00:27:37,510 --> 00:27:40,100
[A sudden farewell...]

340
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:41,400
[Lee Hyeok Jin: See you in the future.]

341
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:45,140
[Taichi: I'll call you when it's over.]
[Park Jae Ha: yes.]

342
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:54,290
[Ending the love at Men's House,
Jae Ha and Hyeok Jin are leaving]

343
00:27:54,300 --> 00:28:00,300
[Lee Hyeok Jin: To me, "His Man" is a program]

344
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:05,460
[Lee Hyeok Jin: where I saw and showed a different side of myself.]

345
00:28:05,460 --> 00:28:11,660
[Lee Hyeok Jin: It's a program where there were things I felt were a pity
and I was really upset in.]

346
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:15,940
[Lee Hyeok Jin: What I want to say to Han Gyeol is]

347
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:22,480
[Lee Hyeok Jin: to thank him for showing interest in me at the start.]

348
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:26,380
[Lee Hyeok Jin: And I want to tell everyone not to feel guilty.]

349
00:28:26,380 --> 00:28:30,060
[Lee Hyeok Jin: To not feel bad about this.]

350
00:28:30,060 --> 00:28:35,720
[Lee Yeonjin: I hope they can follow their hearts sincerely.]

351
00:28:35,720 --> 00:28:43,380
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Hyeok Jin, you've worked hard in your three days in Men's House.]

352
00:28:44,540 --> 00:28:49,220
[Lee Hyeok Jin: There's a future waiting for you. Good luck.]

353
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:57,260
[Park Jae Ha: For me, "His Man" was a coming out]

354
00:28:57,260 --> 00:29:00,860
[Park Jae Ha: and I can view my own expectations more honestly.]

355
00:29:01,360 --> 00:29:05,180
[Park Jae Ha: At least in this program,]

356
00:29:05,180 --> 00:29:08,700
[Park Jae Ha: I showed my true feelings without any hiding.]

357
00:29:08,700 --> 00:29:11,120
[Park Jae Ha: I am quite satisfied.]

358
00:29:13,260 --> 00:29:14,660
[Park Jae Ha: Of course there are regrets.]

359
00:29:14,660 --> 00:29:17,220
[Park Jae Ha: That I can't wrap it up with Hyeong Jun.]

360
00:29:17,220 --> 00:29:20,420
[Park Jae Ha: But no matter it's a good ending or a bad ending,]

361
00:29:20,940 --> 00:29:22,140
[Park Jae Ha: I don't regret it.]

362
00:29:22,140 --> 00:29:27,660
[Park Jae Ha: I think I did everything I could.]

363
00:29:30,500 --> 00:29:35,580
[Very honest and sincere feelings]

364
00:29:42,180 --> 00:29:48,420
[The Men's House that feels
the empty space of the two men]

365
00:29:54,500 --> 00:29:57,240
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Ha...]

366
00:30:13,950 --> 00:30:17,930
[The air in Men's House becomes heavy]

367
00:30:21,380 --> 00:30:23,220
[Kim Han Gyeol: I felt tired in a split second.]

368
00:30:23,220 --> 00:30:26,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was shocked because Hyeok Jin was leaving.]

369
00:30:26,940 --> 00:30:29,540
[Kim Han Gyeol: I felt a little sad that day.]

370
00:30:29,540 --> 00:30:32,740
[Kim Han Gyeol: Everyone has times where they want to be alone.]

371
00:30:32,740 --> 00:30:34,460
[Kim Han Gyeol: That's the time for me.]

372
00:30:40,740 --> 00:30:44,700
[Kim Han Gyeol: Ha.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why? What's on your mind?]

373
00:30:44,700 --> 00:30:46,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm reflecting on myself.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What?]

374
00:30:46,980 --> 00:30:49,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm reflecting on myself.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What are you reflecting on?]

375
00:30:49,100 --> 00:30:52,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm reviewing the past three days.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why?]

376
00:30:54,300 --> 00:30:56,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What's wrong?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm too shocked.]

377
00:30:56,300 --> 00:30:58,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Need to talk?]

378
00:30:58,020 --> 00:31:00,220
[Eum Hyeok Jin: This place is pretty cozy.]

379
00:31:04,340 --> 00:31:06,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I've never talked in a place like that with him.]

380
00:31:06,860 --> 00:31:10,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was thinking if I could]

381
00:31:10,060 --> 00:31:12,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin: speed up my approach to him]

382
00:31:12,740 --> 00:31:15,220
[Eum Hyeok Jin: by talking like this.]

383
00:31:15,220 --> 00:31:17,540
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I needed to confirm my feelings too.]

384
00:31:17,540 --> 00:31:21,500
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm very shocked now.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What's wrong?]

385
00:31:21,500 --> 00:31:26,180
[Kim Han Gyeol: Too many people dislike me.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't think it's dislike.]

386
00:31:26,180 --> 00:31:33,820
[Kim Han Gyeol: If they don't dislike me, it can't be this score.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's not it. It's more like given their standards, you're not of their interest.]

387
00:31:33,820 --> 00:31:35,620
[Kim Han Gyeol: To be honest, I'm very straightforward.]

388
00:31:35,620 --> 00:31:38,460
[Kim Han Gyeol: I don't plan to hide things.]

389
00:31:38,460 --> 00:31:41,340
[Kim Han Gyeol: I asked Taichi if he felt stressed]

390
00:31:41,340 --> 00:31:43,460
[Kim Han Gyeol: and he said no.]

391
00:31:43,460 --> 00:31:45,860
[Kim Han Gyeol: He always gave me "1st" too.]

392
00:31:45,860 --> 00:31:48,620
[Kim Han Gyeol: And we always get along well—that aside.]

393
00:31:48,620 --> 00:31:50,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: But to others,]

394
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:53,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm afraid that they'd think since I already have Taichi...]

395
00:31:53,940 --> 00:31:57,820
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm right, aren't I?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yes, it does feel like that.]

396
00:31:57,820 --> 00:31:59,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But I don't think so.]

397
00:31:59,860 --> 00:32:05,350
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Even so, like I told you just now, I'm just going to try until the end.]

398
00:32:05,350 --> 00:32:10,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You shouldn't be caring about them.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Right.]

399
00:32:10,580 --> 00:32:13,730
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You don't want to date people just cause of what other people think, right?]

400
00:32:13,730 --> 00:32:15,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: So, I've been watching them all this time,]

401
00:32:15,780 --> 00:32:17,860
[Kim Han Gyeol: but I don't know if I'm going in the right direction.]

402
00:32:17,860 --> 00:32:22,700
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's already 40% into the show.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Don't think about that.]

403
00:32:22,700 --> 00:32:26,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The more you think this way, the more shaken you will be
and more thoughts you have.]

404
00:32:26,580 --> 00:32:30,420
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Don't do things that go against your heart.]

405
00:32:30,420 --> 00:32:34,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Do whatever you want.]

406
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:36,420
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'll do the same too.]

407
00:32:36,940 --> 00:32:40,500
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was going to call you today.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Me?]

408
00:32:40,500 --> 00:32:43,500
[Kim Han Gyeol: Seriously.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yes?]

409
00:32:43,500 --> 00:32:49,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: But with Hyeok Jin suddenly eliminated, I'm at a loss.]

410
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:53,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Thank you for saying that.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I mean it.]

411
00:32:53,300 --> 00:32:58,260
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I just wanted to talk like this.]

412
00:32:58,260 --> 00:33:01,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: My goal to talking to you is that]

413
00:33:01,140 --> 00:33:05,250
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I need a confirmation whether I need to continue approaching you.]

414
00:33:11,820 --> 00:33:14,900
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

415
00:33:14,940 --> 00:33:18,900
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The answer yes I can get closer to him.]

416
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:20,540
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That I can approach him legally—]

417
00:33:20,540 --> 00:33:23,340
[Eum Hyeok Jin: it was a moment that gave me confidence.]

418
00:33:23,340 --> 00:33:25,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm grateful for that moment.]

419
00:33:25,860 --> 00:33:28,740
[Kim Han Gyeol: Hyeok Jin accurately knows when I am upset]

420
00:33:28,740 --> 00:33:32,300
[Kim Han Gyeol: and he'd always come to me.]

421
00:33:32,300 --> 00:33:33,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: He really takes care of me.]

422
00:33:33,980 --> 00:33:37,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: I've never seen someone so considerate to me.]

423
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:39,020
[Kim Han Gyeol: Aside from my family.]

424
00:33:43,820 --> 00:33:47,500
[Su Min who's alone in the room
after Jae Ha and Hyeok Jin have left]

425
00:33:54,010 --> 00:34:00,350
[A huge empty space]

426
