641
00:48:36,940 --> 00:48:42,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Luck, timing, opportunities—
none of these went the way I want.]

642
00:48:42,020 --> 00:48:43,980
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why am I the only one getting tested?]

643
00:48:43,980 --> 00:48:47,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Why are you making it harder for me?]

644
00:48:47,620 --> 00:48:53,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: He was always by my side without saying much.]

645
00:48:54,060 --> 00:48:56,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Have fun.]

646
00:48:58,040 --> 00:49:00,400
[Kim Han Gyeol: What will we be doing?]

647
00:49:01,360 --> 00:49:05,140
[The more I care about it,
the more I worry…]

648
00:49:05,140 --> 00:49:07,860
[Sokcho]

649
00:49:10,380 --> 00:49:12,940
[#Sokcho_holiday]

650
00:49:12,940 --> 00:49:14,640
[Dating Freedom Zone]
[Han Gyeol and Taichi came all the way to Sokcho]

651
00:49:17,900 --> 00:49:21,280
[Taichi: Wow, it's my first time coming to see the sea in winter.]

652
00:49:21,280 --> 00:49:26,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: I haven't been to the beach for a long time.
It's nice and warm, isn't it?]

653
00:49:26,100 --> 00:49:29,720
[Taichi: I almost touched the water.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Be careful.]

654
00:49:32,000 --> 00:49:36,460
[Taichi: This is not bad. The thrilling tension.]

655
00:49:36,460 --> 00:49:39,640
[Kim Han Gyeol: But if this continues, I'm going to get wet.]

656
00:49:47,540 --> 00:49:51,960
[Kim Han Gyeol: We came all the way here, and the destination was the sea—
I was quite satisifed.]

657
00:49:52,900 --> 00:49:56,160
[Recording their memories with photos]

658
00:49:58,340 --> 00:50:00,900
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm taking photos.]

659
00:50:07,100 --> 00:50:08,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's square, square. The legs are square.]

660
00:50:16,940 --> 00:50:19,640
[With the winter sea as the background,
they capture a couple photo]

661
00:50:20,140 --> 00:50:21,220
Nice.

662
00:50:22,720 --> 00:50:25,440
[Kim Han Gyeol: I like the smell of the sea.]

663
00:50:25,440 --> 00:50:28,280
[Kim Han Gyeol: I like this smell.]

664
00:50:28,620 --> 00:50:31,680
[Taichi: But it's really beautiful. It's pretty.]

665
00:50:31,680 --> 00:50:33,480
[Kim Han Gyeol: Shall we sit for a while?]
[Taichi: Yeah.]

666
00:50:38,260 --> 00:50:40,020
[Taichi: But it's really beautiful.]

667
00:50:40,020 --> 00:50:44,700
[Taichi: I haven't seen such a beautiful sea for a long time.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's peaceful, right?]

668
00:50:44,700 --> 00:50:46,520
[Taichi: If there is fish, I think I can see it.]

669
00:50:55,020 --> 00:50:58,540
[Taichi: What do you usually talk about
when you're on a date?]

670
00:50:58,540 --> 00:51:03,420
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'll try to get to know their personality
on a date.]

671
00:51:03,420 --> 00:51:05,700
[Kim Han Gyeol: Like what they like]

672
00:51:05,700 --> 00:51:09,300
[Kim Han Gyeol: and what they hope their partner can do for them.]

673
00:51:10,580 --> 00:51:13,140
[Taichi: Let's try it. I'm curious.]

674
00:51:13,140 --> 00:51:15,220
[Kim Han Gyeol: Try what?]
[Taichi: How would you normally talk.]

675
00:51:15,220 --> 00:51:16,700
[Kim Han Gyeol: You want me to ask you questions?]
[Taichi: Mmhmm.]

676
00:51:17,100 --> 00:51:19,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's a Q&A.]

677
00:51:20,060 --> 00:51:24,940
[Taichi: But I'm curious why you approached me at the start.]

678
00:51:25,340 --> 00:51:27,140
[Taichi: So try talking from the beginning.]

679
00:51:27,140 --> 00:51:28,940
[Taichi: Let's try.]

680
00:51:28,420 --> 00:51:28,980
Okay.

681
00:51:28,940 --> 00:51:32,820
[Kim Han Gyeol: Well, what food do you like—I think I asked this before.]
[Taichi: Did you?]

682
00:51:33,140 --> 00:51:35,860
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes, we talked about food.
We talked about beef intestine stew.]

683
00:51:35,860 --> 00:51:38,340
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I know you like fried food.]

684
00:51:38,340 --> 00:51:39,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: I know you like fried food.]

685
00:51:39,940 --> 00:51:43,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: I know your personality.]

686
00:51:45,180 --> 00:51:49,620
[Kim Han Gyeol: Anyway, what I want to ask now is]

687
00:51:49,900 --> 00:51:54,880
[Kim Han Gyeol: when we talked yesterday, I've got the answer.]

688
00:51:55,440 --> 00:52:01,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's nothing special.
We went on dates both yesterday and today.]

689
00:52:02,220 --> 00:52:06,340
[Kim Han Gyeol: Hope it's a good memory for you.]
[Taichi: Yes.]

690
00:52:06,340 --> 00:52:09,580
[Kim Han Gyeol: This is what I hope—not a question.]

691
00:52:15,860 --> 00:52:18,260
[Kim Han Gyeol: What about you?]

692
00:52:21,220 --> 00:52:24,700
[Taichi: How many people are you interested in?]

693
00:52:26,760 --> 00:52:33,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: It's two for now.]

694
00:52:33,100 --> 00:52:35,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: But it's not balanced.]

695
00:52:35,900 --> 00:52:39,360
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm more interested in one of them.]

696
00:52:40,940 --> 00:52:46,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: That's why I was tired and confused yesterday.]

697
00:52:46,380 --> 00:52:48,700
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I went to ask you about it.]

698
00:52:50,180 --> 00:52:53,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: But I hope this rhythm won't change.]

699
00:52:53,760 --> 00:52:56,600
[Han Gyeol confesses his thoughts
in a straightforward manner again]

700
00:52:57,120 --> 00:53:00,880
[Facing Han Gyeol's confession,
Taichi didn't respond immediately]

701
00:53:06,980 --> 00:53:10,540
[Taichi: You mentioned you're interested in two people.]

702
00:53:10,540 --> 00:53:15,440
[Taichi: You said it's not balanced and the level of interest is different,]

703
00:53:19,260 --> 00:53:22,500
[Taichi: right?]

704
00:53:23,240 --> 00:53:25,680
[Kim Han Gyeol: Why? Go on.]

705
00:53:28,980 --> 00:53:32,260
[Taichi: To be honest, I...]

706
00:53:34,580 --> 00:53:38,160
[Taichi: I had the choice today, right?]

707
00:53:38,160 --> 00:53:42,180
[Taichi: Honestly, I hesitated.]

708
00:53:42,180 --> 00:53:48,480
[Taichi: This is how I normally date.]

709
00:53:49,220 --> 00:53:53,660
[Taichi: I easily like people who appeals to me or asks me to go over to them.]

710
00:53:53,660 --> 00:53:57,220
[Taichi: Because I always do that,]

711
00:53:57,220 --> 00:54:00,780
[Taichi: this time round, I wanted to open up my heart
and think about it properly.]

712
00:54:02,220 --> 00:54:05,980
[Taichi: I'm not sure too actually.]

713
00:54:06,340 --> 00:54:11,540
[Taichi: Yesterday and the day before yesterday,
you've been talking to Hyeok Jin.]

714
00:54:11,540 --> 00:54:14,140
[Taichi: I knew it long ago.]

715
00:54:14,460 --> 00:54:19,020
[Taichi: But to be honest, I don't really care.]

716
00:54:23,620 --> 00:54:32,580
[Taichi: I don't think I felt very comfortable seeing the two of you together.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes, I felt that.]

717
00:54:34,540 --> 00:54:37,100
[Taichi: But I'm afraid if...]

718
00:54:37,100 --> 00:54:40,220
[Taichi: if you think I'm avoiding you...]

719
00:54:40,220 --> 00:54:42,940
[Taichi: It's actually because I treat everyone else as a friend.]

720
00:54:43,300 --> 00:54:46,220
[Taichi: But for you and a few of the others,
I still view you as potential date interests.]

721
00:54:46,220 --> 00:54:48,460
[Taichi: But after I gave that a try, I gradually felt]

722
00:54:48,460 --> 00:54:53,100
[Taichi: it got a bit awkward. That's why...
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes, I felt it too.]

723
00:54:53,100 --> 00:54:59,340
[Kim Han Gyeol: When you get along with others,
it feels like you're hanging with friends.]

724
00:55:00,020 --> 00:55:03,660
[Kim Han Gyeol: But you and I don't feel that way.]

725
00:55:06,660 --> 00:55:09,780
[Taichi: When I see the sea, all my emotions sink.]

726
00:55:09,780 --> 00:55:12,700
[Taichi: I just wanted to be honest.]

727
00:55:12,700 --> 00:55:14,580
[Taichi: I don't know why, but I feel guilty.]

728
00:55:14,600 --> 00:55:16,180
[Taichi: But he always liked me]

729
00:55:16,180 --> 00:55:17,440
[Taichi: and always expressed his feelings.]

730
00:55:17,440 --> 00:55:20,360
[Taichi: He took care of me when I went to the beach too.]

731
00:55:20,620 --> 00:55:21,840
[Taichi: So I felt very guilty.]

732
00:55:21,840 --> 00:55:24,500
[Taichi: I hated myself so much.]

733
00:55:24,500 --> 00:55:28,380
[Taichi: Because I can't accept his feelings anymore.]

734
00:55:28,380 --> 00:55:33,460
[Taichi: I've been struggling since this morning—
that I don't have him in my heart.]

735
00:55:33,460 --> 00:55:37,780
[Taichi: So I feel like I'm being arrogant, kinda...]

736
00:55:38,260 --> 00:55:42,680
[Han Gyeol gets what Taichi really feels]

737
00:55:43,960 --> 00:55:47,060
[Kim Han Gyeol: You haven't heard my deepest thoughts, have you?]
[Taichi: Yeah.]

738
00:55:47,060 --> 00:55:50,040
[Kim Han Gyeol: Can I say it?]
[Taichi: Yes.]

739
00:55:51,140 --> 00:55:54,580
[Kim Han Gyeol: We shared a room on the first day.]

740
00:55:54,580 --> 00:55:58,080
[Kim Han Gyeol: Then we separated.]

741
00:55:58,080 --> 00:56:03,240
[Kim Han Gyeol: The other people approached me more proactively.]

742
00:56:04,300 --> 00:56:10,400
[Kim Han Gyeol: At that time, you were 1st place too.]

743
00:56:11,640 --> 00:56:15,440
[Kim Han Gyeol: You're still 1st place now.]

744
00:56:16,520 --> 00:56:19,160
[The two men who miss out on each other]

745
00:56:25,060 --> 00:56:28,160
[Taichi: Maybe it's because I'm still very childish.]

746
00:56:28,520 --> 00:56:30,780
[Taichi: I keep wanting to get close to people]

747
00:56:30,780 --> 00:56:35,120
[Taichi: who like me or I'm interested in.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Of course.]

748
00:56:36,140 --> 00:56:41,100
[Taichi: So I thought about it for a long time,]

749
00:56:41,100 --> 00:56:43,160
[Taichi: when I got the right to go on a date.]

750
00:56:43,860 --> 00:56:46,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: I get that.]

751
00:56:51,500 --> 00:56:52,920
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was not upset.]

752
00:56:52,920 --> 00:56:56,480
[Kim Han Gyeol: I just think people are unpredictable.
You don't know when they will change.]

753
00:56:56,480 --> 00:56:59,720
[Kim Han Gyeol: After all, we haven't known each other for long.]

754
00:57:00,580 --> 00:57:04,780
[Kim Han Gyeol: But it's the first time
Ichi talked to me in such a mature tone.]

755
00:57:04,780 --> 00:57:08,020
[Kim Han Gyeol: I can feel his sincerity.]

756
00:57:08,340 --> 00:57:11,300
[Kim Han Gyeol: So I always felt]

757
00:57:11,300 --> 00:57:13,100
[Kim Han Gyeol: I had a feeling that I couldn't wave away]

758
00:57:13,100 --> 00:57:15,080
[Kim Han Gyeol: previously.]

759
00:57:15,700 --> 00:57:17,820
[Kim Han Gyeol: But being able to say it honestly with the person]

760
00:57:17,820 --> 00:57:20,380
[Kim Han Gyeol: makes me feel relieved.]

761
00:57:20,380 --> 00:57:20,940
Yes.

762
00:57:21,300 --> 00:57:24,280
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm grateful that he told me that too.]

763
00:57:26,640 --> 00:57:32,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: I feel like we've said what we wanted to say.]
[Taichi: Yes. The sea does magic.]

764
00:57:32,980 --> 00:57:34,760
[Kim Han Gyeol: Thank you for telling me.]

765
00:57:35,660 --> 00:57:40,020
[Taichi: Nah. Thanks for listening to me.]

766
00:57:42,060 --> 00:57:46,970
[The time between Han Gyeol and Taichi
was sweet yet beautiful]
